pan></span>)</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.ToMarkdown\">Lean.Doc.ToMarkdown</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.ToMarkdown.mk","kind":"ctor","line":124,"name":"Lean.Doc.ToMarkdown.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L124-L132"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">class</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.ToMarkdown\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">ToMarkdown</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u</div></div>","info":{"doc":"A means of transforming values into Markdown lines.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.ToMarkdown","kind":"class","line":124,"name":"Lean.Doc.ToMarkdown","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L124-L132"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.joinInlines\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">joinInlines</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">parts</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Concatenates a array of lines, where each line is an array of rendered inlines. The last line of one\npiece is glued onto the first line of the next via `glueInlineBoundary` (so `.text \"a\"` followed by\n`.text \"b\"` yields one line `\"ab\"`, but two adjacent `.code` spans get a U+200B between them).\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.joinInlines","kind":"def","line":107,"name":"Lean.Doc.joinInlines","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L107-L122"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.joinBlocks\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">joinBlocks</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">blocks</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Concatenates an array of \"block\" line arrays into one line array, with a single empty separator line\nbetween adjacent non-empty blocks. Empty input blocks are skipped.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.joinBlocks","kind":"def","line":87,"name":"Lean.Doc.joinBlocks","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L87-L95"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.prefixListLines\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">prefixListLines</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">head </span><span class=\"fn\">rest</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">lines</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Applies one prefix to the first line and a different prefix to subsequent lines. Used for list items,\nwhere the first line gets `\"* \"` / `\"1. \"` and the continuation lines get `\"  \"` / `\"   \"`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.prefixListLines","kind":"def","line":76,"name":"Lean.Doc.prefixListLines","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L76-L85"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.prefixLines\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">prefixLines</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">lines</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Applies a uniform prefix to every line. Empty lines receive the trimmed prefix to avoid trailing\nwhitespace (which denotes a hard line break).\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.prefixLines","kind":"def","line":68,"name":"Lean.Doc.prefixLines","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L68-L74"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.MarkdownM.run'\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">MarkdownM</span>.<span class=\"name\">run'</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">act</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.MarkdownM\">MarkdownM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Renders an action that produces an array of lines into a single Markdown string, appending any\naccumulated footnotes after the main body.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.MarkdownM.run'","kind":"def","line":47,"name":"Lean.Doc.MarkdownM.run'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L47-L58"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"br